{"lastModified":1764328777071,"uri":"c::44493161844::vessel::22f5d590-c466-11f0-af62-6162bb2d05ec","yachtType":["Motor"],"description":"Operating Area: Balearics, Spain\n\nEXPLORE MALLORCA IN STYLE\nLUXURY DAY CHARTER ABOARD THE RODMAN R41 FLYBRIDGE\nStep into a world of sun, sea, and elegance aboard our fully equipped Rodman R41 Flybridge, a spacious and powerful motor yacht designed for unforgettable moments along the stunning southwest coast of Mallorca.\n\nDeparting from Port Andratx, one of the island’s most exclusive marinas, you’ll cruise past dramatic cliffs, hidden coves, and turquoise waters on a full-day (8h) private charter. Guided by a professional captain, this is your gateway to secret spots and iconic landmarks like Cala en Egos, Sant Elm, or the natural park of Isla Dragonera.\n\nSoak up the sun on the generous flybridge, dive in for a swim, or explore the sea life with included snorkeling gear. Onboard there’s plenty of space to relax, socialize, or simply take in the Mediterranean views in total comfort.\n\nWhether you're planning a family outing, a romantic escape, or a fun day at sea with friends, the Rodman R41 delivers the perfect balance of performance, comfort, and nautical style.","blueprint":{"name":"EMILY GRACE II","images":["/media/media::image::a::vessel::22f5d590-c466-11f0-af62-6162bb2d05ec::assets::bedd7830-c46d-11f0-9344-2b07eb4d16a9/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::22f5d590-c466-11f0-af62-6162bb2d05ec::assets::bee910f0-c46d-11f0-91bf-0f3240f5364f/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::22f5d590-c466-11f0-af62-6162bb2d05ec::assets::bee36ba0-c46d-11f0-9344-2b07eb4d16a9/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::22f5d590-c466-11f0-af62-6162bb2d05ec::assets::bee31d80-c46d-11f0-9344-2b07eb4d16a9/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::22f5d590-c466-11f0-af62-6162bb2d05ec::assets::bedd9f40-c46d-11f0-9344-2b07eb4d16a9/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::22f5d590-c466-11f0-af62-6162bb2d05